args.new_str:
def probing(rp_log_data_list, rp_question_data_list, labels_log, labels_question, tot_layer):
    list_acc = []
    list_f1 = []
    list_auc = []
    for layer in range(tot_layer):
        # Get hidden states for this layer
        X_log = rp_log_data_list[layer]
        X_question = rp_question_data_list[layer]
        y_log = labels_log
        y_question = labels_question
        # Concatenate log and question representations and labels
        X = np.concatenate([X_log, X_question], axis=0)
        y = np.concatenate([y_log, y_question], axis=0)
        # Split into train/test
        X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(X, y, test_size=0.3, random_state=42, stratify=y)
        # Train logistic regression classifier
        clf = LogisticRegression(max_iter=1000)
        clf.fit(X_train, y_train)
        y_pred = clf.predict(X_test)
        y_prob = clf.predict_proba(X_test)[:,1] if len(clf.classes_) == 2 else None
        # Compute metrics
        acc = accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred)
        f1 = f1_score(y_test, y_pred, average='weighted')
        auc = roc_auc_score(y_test, y_prob) if y_prob is not None else 0.0
        list_acc.append(acc)
        list_f1.append(f1)
        list_auc.append(auc)
    return list_acc, list_f1, list_auc
